b'\xe2\xad\x90\xef\xb8\x8f GIVE LOVE A TRY. The world is so uneasy right now. Why not try to approach a situation/person with love, empathy and mindfulness instead of anger, jealousy or hate. It might not only change the situation but it could end up changing you for the better too! \xf0\x9f\xa4\x8d\xe2\x99\xa5\xef\xb8\x8f\xf0\x9f\xa4\x8d'

b'\xe2\xad\x90\xef\xb8\x8f GO TO THERAPY. Everyone needs someone to talk to without preconceived notions about who you are or whatever situation you\xe2\x80\x99re going through. Truly, it has been the best thing I\xe2\x80\x99ve ever done for myself. (Cont)'

b'\xe2\xad\x90\xef\xb8\x8f DO WHAT MAKES YOU HAPPY. It\xe2\x80\x99s not always going to sit well with people but they don\xe2\x80\x99t have to wake up to your life or any of your choices\xe2\x80\x94you do. So you might as well choose to be happy.'
b'(Cont) Happiness & joy come from being present and being grateful for the beautiful people and gifts we\xe2\x80\x99ve been given. Tomorrow is not promised to any of us. \xf0\x9f\xa4\x8d'

b'\xe2\xad\x90\xef\xb8\x8f HAVE AN ATTITUDE OF GRATITUDE. Society has \xe2\x80\x98destination addiction\xe2\x80\x99 where we\xe2\x80\x99re always focused on the best big thing. If you\xe2\x80\x99re always itching to be somewhere else, you\xe2\x80\x99ll never be content where you are. (Cont)'

b'\xe2\xad\x90\xef\xb8\x8f PROTECT YOUR PEACE. You only have so much energy to give. Be selective about who is deserving of receiving it. You can\xe2\x80\x99t be the well for everyone else if you\xe2\x80\x99re empty. Set your boundaries and stick to them.'
